# docs/ is a local-only SDLC knowledge base — keep it OUT of this public repo
# (PRDs, ADRs, research, decision-log, drafts, QA screenshots, design proofs).
# EXCEPTION: the code-style guide is tracked so the CI auto-reviewer
# (.github/workflows/claude-review.yml) reads the living conventions. Re-including a
# single file requires un-ignoring each parent step, then re-ignoring its siblings.
docs/*
!docs/conventions/
docs/conventions/*
!docs/conventions/code-style.md

# Local git worktrees created by the agent harness (never committed)
.claude/worktrees/

# Playwright MCP scratch (screenshots, snapshots, console logs)
.playwright-mcp/

*.pem
astro/
